OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FAirlines have tightened their rules on
OL,7,Felectronic travel authorisation for UK
OL,8,Fvisitors, leaving many facing the
OL,9,Fpossibility of being refused entry.
OL,11,FAs of February 25, most people who
OL,12,Fcould previously travel to the UK
OL,13,Fwithout a visa now need a digital
OL,14,Fpermission known as an electronic
OL,15,Ftravel authorisation (ETA).
OL,17,FCurrent government advice states that
OL,18,Fvisitors without an ETA will not be
OL,19,Fable to board their transport and
OL,20,Fcannot travel to the UK, unless exempt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
