CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FThere has been limited enforcement of
OL,7,Fthe ETA until now, as it was rolled
OL,8,Fout gradually. It was first introduced
OL,9,Fin 2023 and extended to European
OL,10,Fvisitors in April last year, but has
OL,11,Fnot been strictly enforced.
OL,13,FIt is now mandatory for visitors to
OL,14,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FWhile there were reports of a grey
OL,7,Fperiod, where some airlines may have
OL,8,Fbeen stricter than others in enforcing
OL,9,Fthe ETA rules, several airlines have
OL,10,Fconfirmed to ITV News that they will
OL,11,Fbe following the government guidance
OL,12,Fthat officially came into force on
OL,13,FWednesday.
OL,15,FBritish Airways says it is following
OL,16,FHome Office requirements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
