OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FEasyJet says it "follows the border
OL,7,Frules set down in the jurisdictions
OL,8,Fwhere we operate and we remind
OL,9,Fcustomers before they travel to ensure
OL,10,Fthey have the right documentation for
OL,11,Fthe destinations they are travelling
OL,12,Fto."
OL,14,FAustrian Airlines and Lufthansa say
OL,15,F"it is in each passenger's
OL,16,Fresponsibility that its travel
OL,17,Fdocuments comply with the entry
OL,18,Fregulations for the destination."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FThey go on to say, "If a required
OL,7,Fdocument check of our check-in agent
OL,8,For during the online check-in gives a
OL,9,Fnegative response and is not in line
OL,10,Fwith the regulation in place (e.g.,
OL,11,Ffor the UK), we do not issue a
OL,12,Fboarding pass and inform the passenger
OL,13,Fabout it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
