OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FKLM Royal Dutch Airlines says "an ETA
OL,7,Fmust be obtained if necessary." The
OL,8,Fairline also made clear that "at the
OL,9,Fairport, our ground staff checks
OL,10,Fwhether passengers hold a valid ETA.
OL,11,FIf a passenger does not have the
OL,12,Frequired ETA, we are obliged to deny
OL,13,Fboarding."
OL,15,FWhat is an ETA?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
