OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FETAs act as a digital pre-screening,
OL,7,Fproviding security checks for short-
OL,8,Fterm visitors. Specifically, they
OL,9,Freplace the Electronic Visa Waiver
OL,10,Fsystem, which allowed visa-exempt
OL,11,Fnationals to travel to the UK without
OL,12,Fany prior or checked permissions.
OL,14,FAn ETA will allow non-British passport
OL,15,Fholders without long-stay visas to
OL,16,Ftravel to the UK for tourism, visiting
OL,17,Ffamily, business or short-term study
OL,18,Fpurposes. It only lasts for two years
OL,19,Fbut allows multiple journeys and UK
OL,20,Fstays for up to six months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
