CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FThe new rules apply to people from 85
OL,7,Fcountries, and the government says it
OL,8,Fwill improve the immigration system by
OL,9,Fmaking it a more secure and quicker
OL,10,Fprocess for those crossing the UK
OL,11,Fborder.
OL,13,FThe Home Office says visitors without
OL,14,Fan ETA will not be able to board their
OL,15,Fmode of transport and cannot travel to
OL,16,Fthe UK, unless exempt.
OL,18,FHow to get an ETA
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
