FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772136279
OL,3,CAirlines tighten ETA checks as new
OL,4,Cborder rules come into force
OL,6,FAccording to the Home Office, the
OL,7,Fquickest way to receive an ETA is
OL,8,Fthrough the UK ETA app. But people can
OL,9,Falso apply on its website here.
OL,11,FCurrently, an ETA costs #16, but there
OL,12,Fare plans to increase this to #20.
OL,14,FThe Home Office website says most
OL,15,Fpeople get an automatic decision on
OL,16,Ftheir ETA request within minutes if
OL,17,Fthey apply through the app. But they
OL,18,Frecommend people apply for one at
OL,19,Fleast three working days before
OL,20,Ftravelling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
